    "Central to achieving these ambitious objectives, as depicted in Fig. 2, are the dynamic, interconnected activities of content creation, peer review, and personalized practice sessions-each carefully orchestrated by instructors and enhanced with AI-driven insights and real-time feedback.",
    "To achieve these goals, as shown in Fig. 2, RIPPLE engages students in a trio of intertwined activities of creation, review and personalized practice.",
    "These activities are conducted under the guidance of instructors, complemented by AI-driven real-time feedback and personalized instructions.",
    "Each is outlined in detail below.",
    "RiPPLE actively engages students in the creation of diverse and innovative study resources, a process also known as learnersourcing (Khosravi et al., 2023)."
